    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>sultanas</strong> roughly</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped sultanas </strong>and <strong>grated carrot </strong>to a separate bowl with your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>zingy carrot & sultana slaw</strong></p>",
