    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>ciabatta halves</strong>, cut side down, and cook for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p>",
